{"tid":1242825,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【集思廣益】如何清算黑警種種暴行","createTime":"2019-06-19T08:06:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-19T08:15:02.000Z","uid":127157,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b7a5b53df28c0f5140aeb2f53d36df655a828263","tid":1242825,"uid":127157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T08:06:14.000Z","msg":"監警會今年踏入成立十周年，《蘋果》整理過往9年的統計數字，發現在現行機制下，每年只得3%至4%投訴最終成立，約九成的受罰警員只是被警告或訓諭。數字亦揭露警方視監警會的質詢如「耳邊風」，2017/18年度涉及行使警權的質詢，警方的接受率為0%；至於將投訴結果由不屬實改為屬實的個案，只佔總個案約1%。有民間團體批評監警會是「無牙老虎」，建議授權該會調查嚴重個案，以保障公眾利益。<br />\n<br />\n如題，官方渠道無法申訴，既然投訴無門，就需要動員民間力量，但我地呢啲星斗市民又可以做到啲乜嘢？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190605/59672079?utm_campaign=hkad_article_share&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=share_link\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190605%2F59672079%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_article_share%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dshare_link&d=Ye1L589%2FVCKAmP8JphB8dSQscPELFEQk1IFn5y5IyWs%3D&h=eabe49f4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190605%2F59672079%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_article_share%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dshare_link&h=c7488f70\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190605/59672079?utm_campaign=hkad_article_share&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=share_link</a>"},{"pid":"a09dc78184a0add49fa4ceb85d7f777050ceace9","tid":1242825,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T08:08:30.000Z","msg":"keep住投訴 <br />\n一黎升高個投訴個案但而成功率再拉抵<br />\n二黎開file增加佢地工作"},{"pid":"60abc1c5a92f1e211b7990dc240158ddf0887dce","tid":1242825,"uid":127157,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a09dc78184a0add49fa4ceb85d7f777050ceace9","tid":1242825,